<F P=101> Kosovo </F>
<H3> <TI>   Court Continues To Detain 10 Ethnic Albanians </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0401203094 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 
GMT 4 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0401203094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Republic of Kosova Information Center reports 
that the Supreme Court of Serbia continues to detain 10 Kosovar 
Albanians who were arrested by the Serbian police last November 
on the charge that, allegedly, they and some other persons, as 
members of the Kosova Defense Ministry, made preparations for an 
armed war in Kosova. The counsels of the defendants have 
declared that the arrest of the Albanian youngsters runs counter 
to Serbian laws and this presents another flagrant violation of 
investigation procedures. The counsels of these Albanian 
prisoners have also declared that the defendants are 
continuously tortured by the Serbian police. 

</TEXT>

