December]. The note reciprocates a note from the Czech Foreign 
Ministry of December 22. 
  The cancellation of the fees was initiated at the meeting 
between the Czech and Slovak presidents, Vaclav Havel and Michal 
Kovac, in Lany, Central Bohemia, on November 17. 

