<F P=103> AU0401184994 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest ROMPRES </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Bucharest ROMPRES 4/1/1994 -- Romania's President 
Ion Iliescu received on January 4, 1994, a delegation of the 
North [as received] Korean Daewoo group, led by Kim U-chung, 
chairman of the administration board. 
  The Daewoo group intends to explore ways for large-scale 
investments in Romania in the car-making industry, 
ship-building, refineries, electronics, tourism and the 
