businessmen in cooperation actions in Romania and told his guest 
about the potentialities of the Romanian economy, the 
opportunities created for foreign investors by the Romanian 
legislation. The Romanian president encouraged the 
representives of the Daewoo group to have contacts with Romanian 
businessmen in view of making mutually advantageous transactions. 

