<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Fierce Fighting' Continues in Sarajevo </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0601094094 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 0903 
GMT 6 Jan 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD0601094094 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In Sarajevo, fierce fighting continued this morning 
in the Grbanica district. Heavy fighting is reported round the 
old Jewish cemetery to the south of the city center. Mortar 
explosions, heavy artillery shells and tracer fire pounded the 
area on the Serb-Muslim frontline. According to Sarajevo 
hospitals, 27 persons were killed and 87 wounded in the fighting 
in the last few days. 

</TEXT>

