<F P=102>  LD0501193894 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1335 GMT 5 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0501193894 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


