Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Banja Luka, 5 Jan (TANJUG) -- According to Serb 
military sources, more than 2,000 Albanians are engaged in the 
Muslim army units, fighting in the war against the Serbs in 
former Bosnia-Herzegovina. 
  Military sources in the Srpska republic say that this is a 
realistic number based on testimonies given by captured 
