  [Text] Warsaw, Jan. 7--Press secretary of the prime 
minister Ewa Wachowicz said Friday that the prospect of the 
opening of NATO is not precise. Wachowicz made the remark after 
the Friday meeting between Prime Minister Waldemar Pawlak and 
